<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="著名节操爆表星人" class="zu-question-my-bio">著名节操爆表星人</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="110">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-xiao-chen-51" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-xiao-chen-51" class="zg-link" title="刘晓晨">刘晓晨</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-shui-72" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-shui-72" class="zg-link" title="Appalling">Appalling</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shi-bo-rui-73" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shi-bo-rui-73" class="zg-link" title="石博瑞">石博瑞</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2206106" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">你出去嫖娼，被你老婆抓住。你老婆一哭二闹三上吊，拿着打火机要去开煤气和你同归于尽，这个叫恐怖。<br><br>你在外面轧姘头，你以为你老婆不知道，有一天你在你老婆的床头柜里面无意发现了一叠照片，上面记录着你如何对不起你老婆，还有一把水果刀，这个叫惊悚。<br><br>你把女人领回家，被提前下班的老婆捉奸在床。老婆没骂你，还下厨房做了一桌菜，然后招呼你和姘头一起吃，说来了都是客。<br><br>这个叫<br><br><br>诡异。
<a href="/question/25060124/answer/30251198" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
